  html: `<h1>Hi ${$('Webhook').item.json.body.name},</h1><p>Two weeks in — here's what the top earning members do differently:</p><ol><li><strong>Post consistently.</strong> Members who post 3+ times per week earn 4x more in affiliate commissions. Your content keeps working after you stop.</li><li><strong>Use LinkedIn.</strong> LinkedIn posts drive the highest-value referrals — professionals who are ready to invest in themselves.</li><li><strong>Tell your story.</strong> The most-shared posts are personal wins: a booking, a sale, a goal hit. The AI helps you write it — you just need to share the moment.</li><li><strong>Share your link everywhere.</strong> Your bio, your email signature, your stories. Every touchpoint is a potential commission.</li></ol><p style='margin:24px 0'><a href='https://app.monetura.com/create' style='display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background:#D4A853;color:#2C2420;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:bold'>Create a Post Now</a></p><p>You're a founder. This platform was built for people like you.</p><p>— Darryl</p>`
